::Lord Elder::
   
  Elder sat back, relieved that their mission was finally beginning. He just hoped that they didn't get into trouble at The Ark. History could be destroyed.

Nic <warriorazure@...> wrote:
          Dinobot looked at the two soldiers, then grunted.

Dinobot: I hate fanboys...

Jotunn came in at that moment.

Jotunn: Alright everyone. The attack of the strike force should start
soon, so there's our chance to go unnoticed. Dinobot, please take the
lead.

Dinobot nodded and punched in some instructions on the ship's console.
It lifted and sped up towards north american mainland. 

Dinobot: We should be there soon, but just to make sure, I've
programmed the flight so as to take us far from Relay. We'll keep
quiet about this mission.
